SRC_15273	high	name_desc	src/races_a.c	657	19	Boits are small bipedal creatures covered in yellow, lilac, brown or green fur, distantly related to the Yeeks. Boits move speedily, and can eject the contents of their stomachs at will, but they are not particularly well-suited for melee, ranged combat, use of magical devices, or spellcasting.		me.desc = "Boits are small bipedal creatures covered in yellow, lilac, brown or green "	
