SRC_15282	high	name_desc	src/races_a.c	807	19	Centaur		me.name = "Centaur";	
SRC_15283	high	name_desc	src/races_a.c	808	19	Centaurs are creatures with the head, arms and torso of a human combined with the body and legs of a horse. As such, they are able to move more quickly as they gain experience and are capable of leaping great distances. Centaurs are skilled in fighting and archery and can attack monsters with their hooves in addition to normal melee weapons; but lacking normal feet, they cannot wear boots. Being at home in the forests of the world, Centaurs are able to move quickly through foliage.		me.desc = "Centaurs are creatures with the head, arms and torso of a human combined with the "	
SRC_15284	high	name_desc	src/races_a.c	875	19	Cyclops		me.name = "Cyclops";	
SRC_15285	high	name_desc	src/races_a.c	876	19	With but one eye, a Cyclops can see more than many with two eyes. They are headstrong, and loud noises bother them very little. They are not quite qualified for the magic using professions, but as a certain Mr. Ulysses can testify, their accuracy with thrown rocks can be deadly!		me.desc = "With but one eye, a Cyclops can see more than many with two eyes. They are "	
