SRC_19640	low	other	src/warlock.c	1747	3	Of all the icky, crawling things in the world, you have chosen to make an alliance with spiders? Sure, they are stealthy, and fast, and very adept at hiding. Able to extrude a fine sticky substance to ensnare the unwary, the spider lurks nearby, or so you assume since you very seldom see them. Moreover, many spiders are adept at the powers of teleportation, able to jump quickly from one location to another, which can be quite baffling to a would be predator. They are comfortable with both poison and nexus. They are a bit on the squishy side, though - that is, if you manage to catch one!		"Of all the icky, crawling things in the world, you have chosen to make an alliance "	
