SRC_21643	low	other	src/yeqrezh.c	1623	11	Disciples of Yeqrezh can choose five special gifts, one every ten levels. These gifts can take the form of new abilities, physical powers, or rare items; some can be chosen repeatedly, while others can only be picked once. Once you have selected a gift, you can never go back on your decision, so you might want to study this list to decide which gifts to choose for your character.\n\n		fputs("Disciples of Yeqrezh can choose five special gifts, one every ten levels. "	
